#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:1
msgid "Atlas 300I DUO"
msgstr "Atlas 300I DUO"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:3
msgid "Running vLLM on Atlas 300I DUO"
msgstr "在 Atlas 300I DUO 上运行 vLLM"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:5
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "注意事项"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:7
msgid ""
"The current release supports `FULL_DECODE_ONLY` graph mode on Atlas 300I "
"DUO devices, but the following limitations apply due to hardware event-id"
" resource constraints:"
msgstr ""
"当前版本在 Atlas 300I DUO 设备上支持 `FULL_DECODE_ONLY` 图模式，但由于硬件事件ID资源限制，存在以下限制："

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:9
msgid ""
"When multiple Tensor Parallel (TP) ranks are enabled, the number of "
"capturable graphs is limited and depends on the model depth. For example,"
" Qwen3-32B can capture and replay 2 graphs."
msgstr ""
"当启用多个张量并行（TP）rank时，可捕获的图数量受限，且取决于模型深度。例如，Qwen3-32B 可以捕获并重放 2 个图。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:10
msgid "There is no such limitation when TP=1."
msgstr "当 TP=1 时，不存在此限制。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:11
msgid ""
"We have reached out to the relevant experts for a solution. A software-"
"based fix is considered feasible, but full support will take additional "
"time. Thank you for your understanding."
msgstr ""
"我们已联系相关专家寻求解决方案。基于软件的修复被认为是可行的，但完全支持需要额外时间。感谢您的理解。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:13
msgid "Atlas 300I DUO does not support `triton` or `triton-ascend`."
msgstr "Atlas 300I DUO 不支持 `triton` 或 `triton-ascend`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:15
msgid ""
"If installing from source, `vllm` and `vllm-ascend` will automatically "
"pull in `triton` and `triton-ascend` dependencies, which may cause "
"unexpected issues on Atlas 300I DUO. Please run:"
msgstr ""
"如果从源码安装，`vllm` 和 `vllm-ascend` 会自动引入 `triton` 和 `triton-ascend` 依赖，这可能在 Atlas 300I DUO 上导致意外问题。请运行："

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:24
msgid "Deployment"
msgstr "部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:27
msgid ""
"For Atlas 300I DUO (310P), do not rely on automatic `max-model-len` "
"detection (that is, do not omit the `--max-model-len` argument), or OOM "
"may occur."
msgstr ""
"对于 Atlas 300I DUO (310P)，不要依赖 `max-model-len` 的自动检测（即不要省略 `--max-model-len` 参数），否则可能发生 OOM。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:30
msgid "Reason (current 310P attention path):"
msgstr "原因（当前 310P 注意力路径）："

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:31
msgid ""
"`AscendAttentionMetadataBuilder310` passes `model_config.max_model_len` "
"to `AttentionMaskBuilder310`."
msgstr ""
"`AscendAttentionMetadataBuilder310` 将 `model_config.max_model_len` 传递给 `AttentionMaskBuilder310`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:33
msgid ""
"`AttentionMaskBuilder310` builds a full float16 causal mask with shape "
"`[max_model_len, max_model_len]`, and then converts it to FRACTAL_NZ "
"format."
msgstr ""
"`AttentionMaskBuilder310` 构建一个形状为 `[max_model_len, max_model_len]` 的完整 float16 因果掩码，然后将其转换为 FRACTAL_NZ 格式。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:36
msgid ""
"In the 310P `attention_v1` prefill/chunked-prefill path "
"(`_npu_flash_attention` / `_npu_paged_attention_splitfuse`), this "
"explicit mask tensor is used directly, and there is currently no "
"compressed-mask path."
msgstr ""
"在 310P 的 `attention_v1` prefill/chunked-prefill 路径（`_npu_flash_attention` / `_npu_paged_attention_splitfuse`）中，这个显式的掩码张量被直接使用，目前没有压缩掩码路径。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:41
msgid ""
"If automatic parsing resolves to a large context length, allocating this "
"mask (`O(max_model_len^2)`) may exceed NPU memory and trigger OOM. Be "
"sure to set an explicit and conservative value, such as `--max-model-len "
"16384`."
msgstr ""
"如果自动解析到一个很大的上下文长度，分配这个掩码（`O(max_model_len^2)`）可能会超出 NPU 内存并触发 OOM。请确保设置一个显式且保守的值，例如 `--max-model-len 16384`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:46
msgid "Run the Docker container:"
msgstr "运行 Docker 容器："

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:77
msgid "Note"
msgstr "注意"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:79
msgid ""
"The high performance is implemented based on the latest CANN community "
"edition and the new PTA version. Therefore, you need to manually replace "
"the CANN version with CANN 9.0.0 and torch_npu.The following uses Ubuntu "
"as an example to describe how to install CANN. For details, see the "
"following steps: "
"[Procedure](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/CANNCommunityEdition/900/softwareinst/instg/instg_0090.html?OS=Ubuntu&InstallType=localpack)"
" Install the new PTA version. pip install torch_npu==2.9.0.post2 This "
"step will be supported in v0.18.0.post and later versions. You can ignore"
" it when it is supported."
msgstr ""
"高性能基于最新的 CANN 社区版和新的 PTA 版本实现。因此，您需要手动将 CANN 版本替换为 CANN 9.0.0 和 torch_npu。以下以 Ubuntu 为例介绍如何安装 CANN。详细信息请参见以下步骤：[Procedure](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/CANNCommunityEdition/900/softwareinst/instg/instg_0090.html?OS=Ubuntu&InstallType=localpack) 安装新的 PTA 版本。pip install torch_npu==2.9.0.post2 此步骤将在 v0.18.0.post 及更高版本中得到支持。支持后您可以忽略此步骤。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:82
msgid ""
"Run the following steps to start the vLLM service on NPU for the Qwen3 "
"Dense series:"
msgstr "运行以下步骤在 NPU 上为 Qwen3 Dense 系列启动 vLLM 服务："

