#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:127
msgid "Compression command"
msgstr "压缩命令"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:145
msgid ""
"Argument notes: `--tensor-parallel-size`: `W8A8SC` quantized weights are "
"tightly coupled to the TP size, so you must specify the TP size you plan "
"to use at serving time when running compression. `--model` is the path to"
" the input `w8a8s` weights, and `--output` is the output path for the "
"compressed `w8a8sc` weights."
msgstr ""
"参数说明：`--tensor-parallel-size`：`W8A8SC` 量化权重与 TP 大小紧密耦合，因此在运行压缩时必须指定计划在服务时使用的 TP 大小。`--model` 是输入 `w8a8s` 权重的路径，`--output` 是压缩后 `w8a8sc` 权重的输出路径。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:147
msgid "Additional notes"
msgstr "补充说明"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:149
msgid ""
"The Qwen3-8B model has fewer parameters, so some layers need fallback "
"handling during quantization. It is recommended to download the `qwen3"
"-8B-w8a8sc` weights directly from the Eco-Tech official ModelScope "
"repository once available."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3-8B 模型参数较少，因此某些层在量化过程中需要回退处理。建议在可用时直接从 Eco-Tech 官方 ModelScope 仓库下载 `qwen3-8B-w8a8sc` 权重。"

